txt.en: 'I'm having an adventure. I've paddled all the way from Frogmorton!'
'Are you trying to kill yourself? Get out of the water before you drown!'
'But I'm paddling to the Brandywine! My cousin in Buckland sent me this boat, and I'm going for a visit.'
'You crazy Took, you're as mad as a Baggins!'
'I'm just trying to float my boat down the river. Come down and help me.'
'I'm not getting in there. Besides, you have a hole in the bottom. You're not going anywhere. I know that much!'
